<author>hạny ạ̉nys, qs ạ̉mjd sʿd</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lmạ bkyt mn jrḥ fy qlby lmạ tʿbt ạ̉nạ byn ạ̉ḥzạny
 jyt wrfʿt bạ̹ydk ḥzny jyt wḥnạnk ly mlạny
 ạlqrạr- wḥdk ạ̹nt btgẖny ḥyạty tdy ḍmạn llʿmr ạlậty
 wtkwn ạ̉wjạʿy wậhạty wyạk rby whm srạb
 2- lmạ ạlnạs klhạ nsytny wsṭ ṣʿạb ạlʿmr hnạk
 jyt ttḥnn jyt ḥbtny kl slạmy lqyth mʿạk
 3- lmạ lqytny ạ̉nạ ʿạysẖ wḥdy bạqạsy gẖrbẗ mạlyhạ ậlạm
 jyt bḥnạn bdlt ly krby tẖạbt ʿmry bnhr slạm
 4- lmạ ktyr jrḥwny bsẖdẗ wdmwʿy tzyd wyạ ạ̉nyny
 ḥḍnk kạn ymlạny bqwẗ trjʿ tạny ạnt wtḥyyny</lyrics>
<title>lmạ bkyt mn jrḥ fy qlby</title>
</song>